properties.areaDesc: Cape Fairweather to Cape Suckling Coastal Area
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 31 at 11:17AM AKST until January 31 at 9:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 4 to 6 inches.

* WHERE...Cape Fairweather to Cape Suckling Coastal Area.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM AKST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Reduced visibilities
will adversely impact travel by boat, aircraft, or vehicle.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Bands of snow showers will continue to
train over Yakutat, resulting in additional impactful snow
accumulations through 9 PM AKST.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM AKST THIS EVENING FOR YAKUTAT AND THE NORTHEAST GULF COAST
